title: Withdrawal Acknowledgement Notice Was Sent
body: On June 17, 2021, we received your request to withdraw your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190163933, and completed our review. We mailed you a Withdrawal Acknowledgment Notice. If you do not receive your Withdrawal Acknowledgment Notice by July 17, 2021, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request a copy of the notice. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
